data.text: @Bravotv It was a really bad choice for Carole to say the least. Let’s be clear, the other person who wore it was in a photo/event where everyone was dressed way over the top. Carole looked like she stepped out of an acid trip into a simple dinner with friends.

@Bravotv The day that I start dressing like a Kardashian is the day I shoot myself! They both look ridiculous!!! I would love to see Carole dress classy not trashy just once. I think we would all be surprised how nice she would look. Next time Carole, let Bethenny pick for u not Tinsley.
@Bravotv And it looks ridiculous on both of them 🤣
@Bravotv I just vomited in my mouth.
